<--Versions-->
HTML- 4,5
CSS- 2,3
Javascript- 5,6,7
Bootstrap 4

<--position: sticky-->
{
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
}

<--grid display. If three times auto then it will displayed as 3 columns. Now as one auto it will ocuppy entire width-->
{
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto;
}

<--classlist-->
x.classList.toggle('active');

where x any HTML element.
toggle adds active to className of x element if absent. If active present in classsName it removes it.

<--to get scroll position in Y direction use window.scrollY-->
var x = window.scrollY